Package: fluxModelTemplate
Type: Package
Title: Template Package for fluxCore Models
Version: 1.7.0
Author: Jarrod Dalton [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jarrod Dalton <daltonj@ccf.org>
Authors@R: person(given = "Jarrod",
                  family = "Dalton",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "daltonj@ccf.org")
Description:
    A staged template for developing domain-specific
    entity-level simulation models on top of fluxCore.
    This package is intended to be copied/renamed; it includes
    placeholder shells and a short guide pointing to fluxCore.
